      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALSTON (1) found some support last start but struggled into sixth (19.92), beaten 3.5 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Ready to return to form. RUPESH (3) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Was too tough when scoring last time over 366m at this track in a Restricted WIN (19.80). Has never been out of the money in six starts this distance. One of the prime contenders. CRICKLE OWL VIC (2) did a good job to finish third last time out over 366m at this track (19.93) in a Grade 4/5, the second top-three finish on the trot. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. CHAD POWERS (5) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this circuit.",
